trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs> data includes the <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.Annotation%2A> associated with the event and the <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction> of <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction.Added> or <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction.Deleted>.
trans-unit.target: Le <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs> données incluent le <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.Annotation%2A> associé à l’événement et le <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction> de <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction.Added> ou <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction.Deleted>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="M:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.#ctor(System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction,System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation)" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialise une nouvelle instance de la classe <see cref="M:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.#ctor(System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction,System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation)" />.
<paramref name="annotation" /> ou <paramref name="action" /> a la valeur <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: An action <see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction.Added" /> or <see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction.Deleted" /> value that identifies the operation performed.
trans-unit.target: Une valeur <see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction.Added" /> ou <see cref="F:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentAction.Deleted" /> d'action qui identifie l'opération exécutée.

trans-unit.source: The annotation affected is specified in the <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.Annotation%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: L’annotation affectée est spécifiée dans le <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.Annotation%2A> propriété.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation" /> that changed in the store.
trans-unit.target: Obtient l'<see cref="T:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation" /> qui a été modifiée dans le magasin.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation" /> that changed in the store.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Annotations.Annotation" /> qui a été modifiée dans le magasin.

trans-unit.source: The operation performed with the <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.Annotation%2A> is specified by the <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.Action%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: L’opération effectuée avec la <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.Annotation%2A> est spécifiée par le <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.Storage.StoreContentChangedEventArgs.Action%2A> propriété.
